info.description: .. raw:: html Lino is a high-level framework for writing desktop-like customized database applications based on `Django `_ and `Sencha ExtJS `_. Lino applications are Django projects where the application developer does not need to write any URLconf, HTML nor CSS (`more `__). Examples of Lino applications are `Lino Welfare `__, `Lino Così `__ or `Lino Voga `__ (`more `__) The central project homepage is http://www.lino-framework.org
info.name: lino
info.summary: A framework for writing desktop-like web applications using Django and ExtJS
